snippet.title: orbt - Free Android / iOS game (Trailer 2016)
snippet.description:
Download for Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.NVS.orbt
Download for iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/orbt-gravity-defying-action/id1149657103

Touch the screen to move your planet, don't get sucked into the black holes or run into any obstacles. Survive as long as you can.
